EXAMINATIONS HAVE BEEN COMPLETED THROUGH 1997 AND INCOME TAXES HAVE BEEN SETTLED WITH THE IRS FOR ALL YEARS THROUGH 1996 AND FOR MCDONNELL DOUGLAS CORPORATION FOR ALL YEARS THROUGH 1992. WE HAVE FILED APPEALS WITH THE IRS FOR 1993 THROUGH 1997 FOR

MCDONNELL DOUGLAS CORPORATION.

