APPROVED BCCS UNSECURED CLAIM AGAINST THE HAWAIIAN ESTATE AND ALSO APPROVED THE NEW TERMS OF ITS RESTRUCTURED LEASES. IN SEPTEMBER 2004, BCC SOLD ITS UNSECURED CLAIM TO RC AVIATION LLC (RANCH). IN CONNECTION WITH THE APPROVAL OF ITS CLAIM BY

