THE CLAIM. PRIOR TO HAWAIIANS BANKRUPTCY, BCC ACCOUNTED FOR ALL OF ITS 717 LEASES AND TWO OF ITS THREE 767 LEASES AS FINANCE LEASES. SUBSEQUENT TO THE APPROVAL OF THE RESTRUCTURED LEASE TERMS, BCC WILL CONTINUE TO ACCOUNT FOR THESE LEASES AS

FINANCE LEASES.

