BANKRUPTCY COURT, SET FORTH THE TERMS UNDER WHICH ALL 14 AIRCRAFT FINANCED BY BCC ARE EXPECTED TO REMAIN IN SERVICE UPON HAWAIIANS EMERGENCE FROM CHAPTER 11 PROTECTION.

