DECISION TO RETAIN THE AIRCRAFT IN OUR EXECUTIVE FLEET. DURING THE SAME PERIOD OF 2003, BCC RECOGNIZED CHARGES OF $121 MILLION, OF WHICH $21 MILLION WAS DUE TO THE

