CURRENTLY, ASTRO LTD. INSURES AVIATION LIABILITY, WORKERS COMPENSATION, GENERAL LIABILITY, PROPERTY, AS WELL AS VARIOUS OTHER SMALLER RISK LIABILITY INSURANCES.

