REQUESTED LEASE OR LOAN RESTRUCTURINGS; THESE NEGOTIATIONS WERE IN VARIOUS STAGES AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2004.

·

DURING 2003, BCC COMPLETED A RESTRUCTURING OF UNITED AIRLINES, INC. (UNITED) AIRCRAFT LOANS AND LEASES. UNITED ACCOUNTED FOR $1,131 AND $1,159 (10% AND 11%) OF OUR

AIRCRAFT FINANCING PORTFOLIO AT DECEMBER 31, 2004 AND 2003. THE TERMS OF THE RESTRUCTURED LOANS AND LEASES RESULTED IN A CHARGE TO THE VALUATION ALLOWANCE OF $50.

