PORTFOLIO AND RECORDED A CHARGE OF $180 ($100 RECOGNIZED AT BCC) TO INCREASE THE VALUATION ALLOWANCE DUE TO DETERIORATED AIRLINE CREDIT RATINGS AND DEPRESSED AIRCRAFT VALUES BASED ON OUR QUARTERLY ASSESSMENT OF THE ADEQUACY OF CUSTOMER FINANCING

RESERVES.

