INCOME RECOGNIZED ON SUCH RECEIVABLES DURING THE PERIOD IN WHICH THEY WERE CONSIDERED IMPAIRED WAS $30, $106 AND $18 FOR THE YEARS ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2004, 2003 AND 2002, OF WHICH $35, $115 AND $12 WAS RECOGNIZED ON A CASH BASIS, RESPECTIVELY.

