BCCS PORTFOLIO AT DECEMBER 31, 2004 AND 2003, TOTALED $9,680 AND $10,118. THE DIFFERENCE BETWEEN BCCS TOTAL ASSETS AND PORTFOLIO IS PRIMARILY CASH AND ASSETS

